description.content:
Transform your vision into a working product!



I am a Full-Stack Mobile and Web developer ( React Native, React JS, Next JS, Node JS, AWS, MongoDB, Firebase, My Sql) with more than 4 years of professional experience with different technology stack.


Solid experience in the development of E-commerce, CRM, Cloud platforms, social networking apps, news portals, high-load platforms, and facility management platforms.


Speciality:


E-commerce, Social Media Apps, Logistics, Restaurant App, Food Delivery App, News Portal, Blogging, ERP Solutions, Payment Gateways (Stripe, Paypal, Google Pay, Apple Pay), Facebook Graph API integration, Google Maps Integration and much more


Tech Stack:


I feel confident to work with:


Frontend technologies :

JavaScript, React Native, React JS, Next JS, HTML, CSS


Backend technologies:

Node.js, Express, AWS, MongoDB, Firebase, MySql


Feel free to get in touch with me if you have any questions.


I am looking forward to working with you!
